show.description: While investigating a brutal attack in Mumbai, a fearless young lawyer unexpectedly steps into a hidden world. Without her knowledge, she ends up marrying a powerful werewolf. Now, she stands at a crossroads should she choose the path of justice, or embrace the shadowy realm of love and destiny? A thrilling tale of courage, secrets, and forbidden love.
